steamworks-sdk provides CMake targets:

    find_package(SteamworksSDK CONFIG REQUIRED)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE Steamworks::API)
    # Optional: encrypted app ticket library
    # target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE Steamworks::EncryptedAppTicket)

Note: Building requires a valid steamLoginSecure cookie from a Steamworks partner account.
Export it before building:

    export STEAM_LOGIN_SECURE="<your steamLoginSecure cookie>"
